sp.p:
satrāsotkampam
ajjaütta! parittāāhi, parittāāhi!āryaputra! paritrāyasva, paritrāyasva!
)

sabhayam
mahābhāa! ahiṃsā palamo dhammo! hiṃsā palamo adhammo!mahābhāga! ahiṃsā paramo dharmo! hiṃsā paramo 'dharmaḥ!
)

saromāñcam
aho arihanta! aho arihanta! kāvālinīe phalasasuhaṃ! aï, sundali! dedu! dedu! dāva puṇo aṅkapāliṃ! svagatam are, mahanto khu indiaviālo saṃvutto! tā kiṃ ettha juttaṃ? bhodu | picchiāe ḍhakissam |aho arhanta! aho arhanta! kāpālinyāḥ sparśasukham | aye, sundari! dadātu! dadātu! tāvat punar aṅkapālim! are, mahān khalv indriyavikāra saṃvṛtttaḥ! tasmād kim atra yuktam? bhavatu | picchikayā sthagayiṣye |
)
